{"tid":586275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「本土派」KOL針對范國威       范國威回應","createTime":"2018-03-09T11:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T05:04:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"524c6ac8b7e7df9a8a8c4c950c31ed9899354fe2","tid":586275,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0dd215357ccc561c4e93ef7a6a6f9ae8_pyMS9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0dd215357ccc561c4e93ef7a6a6f9ae8_pyMS9_1200x0.png&h=0405d158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會補選將於本周日舉行，非建制派分歧仍然嚴重。不少本土派人士近日在網上呼籲選民，寧可把選票「射落海」也不要支持民主派候選人，實行所謂的「焦土」策略，並將矛頭直指經常以「務實本土」自居的新民主同盟范國威。<br />\n<br />\n范國威被圍攻<br />\n<br />\n《豬場新聞》在其facebook專頁以「投范國威不如射落海好過」為題，措詞強硬指責范國威是「虛偽、唯利是圖」的「無恥政棍」，為了選舉而自稱「本土派」，但卻針對「光復行動」，不滿范在梁游被DQ當日立刻表示考慮參與補選。文中又指，范國威當年堅決反對民主黨密會中聯辦致令超級區議會成事，最後退黨自立門戶，他藉著這個「光環」贏得2012年立法會議席，但2016年卻併棄「民主原則」、派人參選超區。「真係投唔落手，睇返成個選舉，我都係射落海算。」<br />\n<br />\n帖文留言有網民建議，會把票「直接投對家」，有部份人留言指會投白票，有人笑稱「識投一定投娥姐」。但亦有網民斥責若因不滿泛民而投「對家」，導致建制派最後勝出，後患更是無窮。「投泛民同建制有咩分別!? 分別咪係泛民要向選民交待囉!? 你試下聽日立廿三條邊個幫你投反對票？射落海對自己有咩好處呀？對家係唔會因為你射落海而對你手下手下㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n范國威日前接受《蘋果日報》專訪，表示希望能獲得曾在新東補選支持梁天琦的選民認同，又說決定吸納民主派初選對手張秀賢支援抗爭者的主張，承諾當選的話，將撥出議辦資源協助在囚抗爭者和囚權問題，並會向政府提出改善在囚人士權益。<br />\n<br />\n《墳場新聞》總編青永屍也在facebook發帖文，斥責范國威當日對被捕本土派支持者「落井下石」，今天在梁天琦成階下囚時，卻求票於本土派。「下？天琦仲坐緊，大棚人等緊審，你當日譴責、割蓆；落井下石。今日求票？玩呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">范國威回應《立場新聞》查詢，認為自己初選後吸納部份張秀賢的本土主張。他又認為行動重要過說話，過去新民主同盟有為支援抗爭者籌款，亦有探訪13+3的抗爭者，14日將會去探望社民連副主席黃浩銘。對於各方批評，范國威稱更想專注實務上工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港焦土力量　翻區諾軒舊帳<br />\n<br />\n另一本土facebook專頁《香港焦土力量》，也諷刺2016年泛民拒簽選管會確認書抗政治篩選，但今次補選卻全部泛民也有簽署確認書。<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒曾經被指，在2015年區選期間，在一個民主黨WhatsApp群組中發表侮辱「青年新政」的言論，揶揄對方是在「派發免費一樓一指南」。《香港焦土力量》亦舊事重提，「我就乜都唔知，淨係記得個陣區諾軒見青年新政選九龍西，就係咁笑鳩人地輸硬，仲建議游蕙禎企街派叫雞指南先有機會贏咁喎」。<br />\n<br />\n香港輔仁媒體總編輯容樂其昨日也發帖表達不滿，指建制派即使「做戲」，至少尚算客氣，民主派想本土派投票卻態度不佳。「建制派啲鐵票，素來都無預我，都尚且會對我客客氣氣。反對派要我張票，都串過馬撚。理念大志我讀書少唔識理解，我只知道邊個對我好，就算呢個『好』，係做戲，係扮，起碼佢地都仲會對我笑下。」<br />\n<br />\n中出羊子：識投一定投共<br />\n<br />\n容樂其在其個人專頁上，又分享了不少本土派人士有關補選投票意向的帖文，其中包括有「昭明公主」之稱、於2016年立法年選舉曾報名參選新西直選，但因主張香港獨立而被選舉主任褫奪參選資格的中出羊子。其帖文指，寧可票投建制派，也絕不投泛民：「識投，一定投共！投井、投河、投降都唔撚投泛民。」<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：泛民是「greater evil」<br />\n<br />\n有「國師」之稱的陳雲根下午發文，指泛民是「greater evil」(更大的惡)，不是「lesser evil」(更小的惡)，更指「沒有泛民，政府作不了惡」。他在文中指不要再「自欺欺人」，「要入共產黨的棺材，不必請泛民幫你做壽衣的。壽衣你自己本來就有，為什麼要付一筆裁縫費給泛民在上面釘上&ldquo;我要真普選&rdquo;呢？」<br />\n<br />\n早前他又在專頁上發帖，指當中共修憲走向帝制，過去抗爭方法經已失效，包括投票給泛民。他寫道：「一個時代過去，中共走向帝制。一切以前的政治鬥爭方法，包括投票給泛民，已經失效，甚至令香港死得更慘。可惜，香港人仍以為自己活在英治時代，仍不願醒來。 」<br />\n<br />\n另外，「門徒事工」認為不應積極參與因DQ而觸發的「不義」補選，發起杯葛投票行動表達不不妥協立場。不過在其專頁《門徒媒體》，大多留言均表示不認同意做法，認為會增加建制勝算，更有網民說本不打算投票，但由於出現杯葛行動，反而改變主意將會投票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/補選焦土派-本土派kol狙擊泛民-籲寧-射落海-投建制-特別針對范國威/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8%E7%84%A6%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE-%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BEkol%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91-%E7%B1%B2%E5%AF%A7-%E5%B0%84%E8%90%BD%E6%B5%B7-%E6%8A%95%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%2F&d=CLTC44eENDWC4%2FMg%2FfkLu5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=3b70aa51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8%E7%84%A6%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE-%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BEkol%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91-%E7%B1%B2%E5%AF%A7-%E5%B0%84%E8%90%BD%E6%B5%B7-%E6%8A%95%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%2F&h=e2610a70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/補選焦土派-本土派kol狙擊泛民-籲寧-射落海-投建制-特別針對范國威/</a>"},{"pid":"48a81202697ce6e7b8216a682fb244a2e3333595","tid":586275,"uid":12565,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"你哋泛民淨係聲援所有在囚抗爭者咋<br />\n泛民果陣遊行叫本土派出嚟，但係籌錢淨係幫泛民果13+3 咋屌你老母<br />\n仲扮以前有支援過本土派我屌你啦"},{"pid":"dbf0f9ba8f62af8409a8085804ea0ec88c7ac4f0","tid":586275,"uid":34223,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"含撚嘅方法有好多 但係一定唔含犯蟈威"},{"pid":"f19d1cb8519182f5b8a4ed985db7f5f3f71558cf","tid":586275,"uid":34869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"13+3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲話自己本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcee9295805f154d7feb9f2483d93b2e5474258e","tid":586275,"uid":88999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"13+3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"fb5d28ad0d98b3034ede3e0411ddf44a316d97e5","tid":586275,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"13+3要天琦票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9677facc00d89ae9d041fc08f8502dd6b667ffb","tid":586275,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:20:18.000Z","msg":"范國閪呢隻典型港閪 <br />\n畀佢做到一屆就現哂形<br />\n邊個再投畀佢入議會真係賤過袋底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3720cb40f98c21f5ce73eec9d78d3ba99ad4fee","tid":586275,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f19d1cb8519182f5b8a4ed985db7f5f3f71558cf","tid":586275,"uid":34869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"13+3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲話自己本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"好心佢諗清楚先答啦<br />\n連人哋屌緊佢乜都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e258e08536ad30daba803f665a18374a687b19","tid":586275,"uid":21392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"射落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc48898936f6a4f5112af61486bb695f4f7d520","tid":586275,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"立場一次過QUOTE晒屌范國威嘅人，<br />\n最想佢輸嘅人可能係泛民中人。"},{"pid":"9ea8094a623aaef3f7d2ce326d292b97eed96a55","tid":586275,"uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爭取家庭團聚審批權聯署聲明</span>[/b]<br />\n來源：[url]<a href=\"http://www.ipkinyuen.org.hk/wordpress/?p=432&amp;lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipkinyuen.org.hk%2Fwordpress%2F%3Fp%3D432%26lang%3Dzh&d=CLTC44eENDWC4%2FMg%2FfkLu5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=59ab410e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ipkinyuen.org.hk/wordpress/?p=432&amp;lang=zh</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n2013年11月1日<br />\n<br />\n一、 我們認為家庭團聚是國際基本人權，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支持維持以家庭團聚為目的的單程証配額</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n二、 我們要求特區政府應取回或參與入境審批權，使審批制度能彰顯家庭團聚的原則 。<br />\n<br />\n三、 我們認為香港社會應<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以包容、公義的原則對待新來港人士，不應將他們視為掠奪香港資源的負累</span></strong>。我們支持一個更團結及更民主的香港，不<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認同任何排外和分化的言行</span></strong>，並將致力促進香港社會堅守公平和包容的原則 。<br />\n<br />\n四、我們認為政府應制訂長遠人口政策，因應人口變化做好房屋、福利、教育及就業等配套。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>聯署立法會議員</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n李卓人、何秀蘭、張超雄、張國柱、何俊仁、劉慧卿、單仲偕、胡志偉、涂謹申、黃碧雲、梁家傑、湯家驊、郭家麒、陳家洛、郭榮鏗、莫乃光、馮檢基、梁繼昌、葉建源、李國麟、梁耀忠、梁國雄<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>聯署團體</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n同根社、影子長策會、土地正義聯盟、社會民主連線、關愛長者大聯盟、香港基督徒學會、街坊工友服務處、關注基層住屋聯席、香港專上學生聯會、關注綜援低收入聯盟、關注中港家庭權利聯席、關注學童發展權利聯席、關注跨境兒童權益聯席、香港天主教正義和平委員會、丘文俊議員辦事處、容溟舟議員辦事處、[b]<span style=\"color: red;\">新民主同盟</span>"},{"pid":"f6347dc7d4384489681454a51a01ff0fdc08bfe6","tid":586275,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">13+3</span></span>"},{"pid":"c30b969b3633ade4cffd0d1b3bee26b32c090c7a","tid":586275,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf6b9897418a62566880f92035c9399c9bb02b3","tid":586275,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"邊個屌泛民, 未來撚啊廢就會屈你係五毛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/586528/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/586528/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"218a7520d71ef8d12dda2a8cc48e1fad5d3567d8","tid":586275,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"容癌、國屍都話要焦土，代表啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991e6ab9cb992ac1a7348079b03ed5727b9fe1c5","tid":586275,"uid":66324,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"我唔認同投對家, 亦都唔好投白票, 投果陣一定要cup到張票花哂, 唔好比位人造馬<br />\n投對家即係endorse左果邊, 令佢有更大牙力, 反而投廢票係順其自然<br />\n投票係投比能夠代表你的候選人, 既然無人代表到你應該投廢票"},{"pid":"370fa8bea20362c30eef490807ebcbfbc9d3a5d6","tid":586275,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"投廢票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0affeac6f47d7a05a5c4c0763b1c8dfd162e062","tid":586275,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"2b7588e923611627c32c5e2ab0fb5f3abdcfb581","tid":586275,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"